268
00:19:53,752 --> 00:19:54,650
What?!

269
00:20:01,760 --> 00:20:03,990
Mind Destruction Jutsu, a success.

270
00:20:11,236 --> 00:20:13,704
All right, you did it, Ino!

271
00:20:14,406 --> 00:20:17,432
Damn it!
