<i>Sail across a thousand dreams</i>

300
00:22:16,862 --> 00:22:19,729
<i>Running freely</i>

301
00:22:19,798 --> 00:22:23,359
<i>To take hold of the world in hand</i>

302
00:22:23,468 --> 00:22:26,460
<i>The clouds scatter</i>

303
